We employ committed investment professionals from different nationalities, and career backgrounds on planet Earth working across
 the full investment life cycle including the origination and execution of new investments and the management of our growing portfolio.
 
Tasks
 
 
 Evaluation, structuring and negotiation of investment opportunities 
 Perform detailed asset valuation, financial analysis and benchmarking 
 Perform buy-side due diligence across commercial, technical, legal and other due diligence areas 
 Liaising with key counterparties including advisers, lenders and corporate representatives 
 Preparation of investment approval documents and participation in 
 
investment committee meetings
 
 Support existing investments, including monitoring of ongoing financial and operational performance, performing valuations and preparing documentation in advance of board meetings 
 Monitoring the activities and performance of competitor companies 
 
